===气候===
根据[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，阿卡胡特拉属于[[熱帶乾濕季氣候|熱帶乾濕季氣候]]。与其他中美洲{{tsl|en|Pacific Coast|太平洋沿岸}}的国家相同，阿卡胡特拉的气候炎热且潮湿，白天的温度通常能达到32°C至34°C<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=5687&cityname=Acajutla%2C+Sonsonate%2C+El+Salvador&units= |title=Climate Summary for Acajutla |access-date=2019-01-18 |archive-date=2019-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930223543/http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=5687&cityname=Acajutla%2C+Sonsonate%2C+El+Salvador&units= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

